ng/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/75.mp3","time_start":220.75,"time_end":225.85},{"position":76,"content":"Is that like yours?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/76.mp3","time_start":225.85,"time_end":227.07},{"position":77,"content":"Yes, that's how most of them are.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/77.mp3","time_start":227.41,"time_end":230.19},{"position":78,"content":"Well, the first thing is cancellation.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/78.mp3","time_start":230.19,"time_end":232.52},{"position":79,"content":"If the holiday's cancelled on the policy I've got, you can claim £8,000.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/79.mp3","time_start":232.52,"time_end":237.37},{"position":80,"content":"We can improve on that, Ms Nash.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/80.mp3","time_start":237.55,"time_end":239.81},{"position":81,"content":"For Greek Island holidays, our maximum is £10,000.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/81.mp3","time_start":240.37,"time_end":244.48},{"position":82,"content":"That's good - of course our holiday won't even cost £1,000 together!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/82.mp3","time_start":244.48,"time_end":249.56},{"position":83,"content":"It's still sensible to have good cover.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/83.mp3","time_start":249.75,"time_end":252.35},{"position":84,"content":"Now, if you go to hospital, we allow £600.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/84.mp3","time_start":252.52,"time_end":256.21},{"position":85,"content":"Yes, mine's similar.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/85.mp3","time_start":256.21,"time_end":257.4},{"position":86,"content":"And we also allow a relative to travel to your holiday resort.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/86.mp3","time_start":257.72,"time_end":261.59},{"position":87,"content":"My policy just says their representative will help you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/87.mp3","time_start":261.59,"time_end":264.99},{"position":88,"content":"You can see there's another difference there.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/88.mp3","time_start":265.61,"time_end":267.61},{"position":89,"content":"And what happens if you don't get on the plane?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/89.mp3","time_start":267.92,"time_end":270.6},{"position":90,"content":"Nothing, as far as I can see on this form.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/90.mp3","time_start":270.6,"time_end":273.68},{"position":91,"content":"Don't you have missed departure?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/91.mp3","time_start":273.96,"time_end":277.11},{"position":92,"content":"No, I'll just jot that down.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/92.mp3","time_start":277.23,"time_end":280.23},{"position":93,"content":"We pay up to £1,000 for that, depending on the reason.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/93.mp3","time_start":280.49,"time_end":284.95},{"position":94,"content":"And we're particularly generous about loss of personal belongings -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/94.mp3","time_start":284.95,"time_end":288.99},{"position":95,"content":"up to £3,000, but not more than £500 for a single item.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/95.mp3","time_start":288.99,"time_end":293.99},{"position":96,"content":"Then I'd better not take my laptop!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/96.mp3","time_start":293.99,"time_end":296.12},{"position":97,"content":"Not unless you insure it separately.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/97.mp3","time_start":296.12,"time_end":298.33},{"position":98,"content":"Okay, thanks very much for your time, you've really been helpful.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/98.mp3","time_start":298.33,"time_end":302.05},{"position":99,"content":"Can I get back to you? Your name is?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/99.mp3","time_start":302.05,"time_end":305.03},{"position":100,"content":"Ben Ludlow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/100.mp3","time_start":305.03,"time_end":306.77},{"position":101,"content":"That's LUDLOW.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/101.mp3","time_start":306.77,"time_end":310.67},{"position":102,"content":"I'm the Assistant Manager here.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/102.mp3","time_start":310.67,"time_end":312.8},{"position":103,"content":"I'll give you my number.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/103.mp3","time_start":312.8,"time_end":314.31},{"position":104,"content":"It's 081260543216.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/104.mp3","time_start":314.31,"time_end":323.15},{"position":105,"content":"But didn't I phone 081260567294?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/105.mp3","time_start":323.15,"time_end":330.31},{"position":106,"content":"That's what I've got on the paper.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/106.mp3","time_start":330.31,"time_end":332.03},{"position":107,"content":"That's the main switchboard.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/107.mp3","time_start":332.03,"time_end":333.75},{"position":108,"content":"I've given you my direct line.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/108.mp3","time_start":333.75,"time_end":335.73},{"position":109,"content":"Right, thank you very much for your time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-9-test-3-part-1-2023-07-23-15-04-38/109.mp3","time_start":335.73,"time_end":338.33}]}